## Quick Recap

| Object | Represents | Example |
|--------|-----------|---------|
| **Account** | A Company | Apple Inc. |
| **Contact** | A Person | Tim Cook (at Apple Inc.) |
| **Opportunity** | A Deal/Sale | Apple - iPhone Supply Deal ($50M) |

**Remember:** Without Accounts and Contacts, you can't have Opportunities. The three objects work together to form the foundation of CRM.

